                     go to exe-pgm-frg-400
           else      go to exe-pgm-frg-500.
       exe-pgm-frg-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se sort non eseguito                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
